<h3>Managing at Group Level</h3>
<hr>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-5 col-sm-4 col-lg-3">
    {{ui-buttons
      type='radio'
      buttons='Foo,Bar,Baz'
      disabled='baz'
      moodActive='success'
      defaultValue='bar'
    }}
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-lg-4 monospace">
  <b>\{{ui-buttons </b><br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;buttons='Foo,Bar,Baz' <br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;type='radio'<br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;disabled='baz'<br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;moodActive='success'<br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;defaultValue='bar'<br/>
  }}
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-lg-5">
    Here we see the more compact yet highly capable inline form of the component. A things to take note of:
    <ul>
      <li><b>CSV Loading</b> - for many properties which can take on multiple values you can obviously bind to an array in the container but you may also use a CSV string in the template to load the values. Here you see that in <code>buttons</code> and <code>disabled</code>.</li>
      <li><b>Global Properties</b> - properties like <code>moodActive</code> (as well as <code>size</code> and others)</li>
    </ul>
    More on these properties later ...
  </div>
</div>
<hr>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-xs-5 col-sm-4 col-lg-3">
    {{ui-buttons
      type='radio'
      buttons='Foo,Bar,Baz'
      size='small'
      moodActive='warning'
      defaultValue='bar'
    }}
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-3 col-sm-3 col-lg-4 monospace">
  <b>\{{ui-buttons </b><br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;buttons='Foo,Bar,Baz' <br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;type='radio'<br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;disabled='baz'<br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;moodActive='success'<br/>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;defaultValue='bar'<br/>{{#if size}}
  &nbsp;&nbsp;size='{{size}}'<br/>{{/if}}
  <b>}}</b>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-lg-5">
    Now we'll give you a little playground to play around with a few other parameters:
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-3">size</div>
      <div class="col-xs-9">
        {{ui-buttons buttons=sizes size='small' type='radio' value=size}}
      </div><br/>
      <div class="col-xs-3 downer">canBeEmpty</div>
      <div class="col-xs-9 downer">
        {{ui-buttons buttons=canBeEmpty  size='small' type='radio'}}
      </div><br/>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

